        <methods>
            <methodStep>
                <description>
                    <para>Records of native and naturalised plants and animals have been collated from RHS gardens and some surrounding areas since 1909. Data has been gathered from various sources, including paper archives and the RHS insect collection. Many modern records (post 1997) have been submitted directly to the Recorder software.</para>
                </description>
            </methodStep>
            <qualityControl>
                <description>
                    <para>Data quality is good. Most records are verified by expert RHS staff members. Grid references have been checked against site names.</para>
                </description>
            </qualityControl>
        </methods>

